        public <R> EventActionBuilder<E,R> finishWithResult(java.util.function.Function<E,R> finisher)
        Description copied from interface: EventActionBuilder
        Sets a Function that runs after the stopper is called with the Event as the parameter, producing an Object. This allows the EventActionFuture to return a Result when it finishes waiting for events.
